  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "These chatd tests are flaking for the same stale control-notification race tracked by CODAGT-353, so this change skips the newly reflaking advisor-chain and `TestPatchChatMessage/ChangesModel` tests and rewrites the older `TODO(hugodutka)` skips to point at the same root cause. This keeps the known flakes documented consistently until the chatd notification-flow refactor lands.\n\nCloses CODAGT-427\nCloses https://github.com/coder/internal/issues/1510\n",
